        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Broadband Conduit Deployment Act of 2018</strong></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Transportation to require states to evaluate the need to install broadband conduit in any project to construct a new highway or additional lane or paved shoulder for an existing highway that is begun after the enactment of this bill and that receives funding under the federal-aid highway program. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
